<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Signup</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #87CEFA, #00BFFF);
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .sidebar {
            background: #1E90FF;
            color: white;
            width: 40%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -40%;
            height: 100vh;
            animation: slideIn 1s forwards;
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure sidebar is above other content */
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            to {
                left: 0;
            }
        }

        .sidebar h3 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-family: 'Lucida Handwriting', 'Comic Sans MS', cursive;
        }

        .sidebar p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .sidebar ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .sidebar ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a {
            color: #f7f4f4;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a:hover {
            color: #1E90FF;
        }

        .main-content {
            margin-left: 40%;
            width: 60%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .form-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00BFFF;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: border 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus {
            border-color: #00BFFF;
            outline: none;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: #00BFFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #1E90FF;
        }

        h5 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        h5 a {
            color: #00BFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        h5 a:hover {
            color: #1E90FF;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h3>Welcome to ArtZone</h3>
        <p>
            Explore, discover, and purchase unique pieces of art from talented artists worldwide. Follow the guidelines to ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience on our platform.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#">If you are want to upload arts on the website, Please choose your role as Artist</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">If you want to buy arts from our website, Please choose your role as Customer</a></li>
          <h3><li class="bold">Art is something that makes you breathe with a different kind of happiness</li></h3>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="form-container">
            <h2>Signup</h2>
            <form action="/signup" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="username" placeholder="Enter your name" required autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="gender">Gender:</label>
                    <select id="gender" name="gender" required>
                        <option value="">Select your gender</option>
                        <option value="male">Male</option>
                        <option value="female">Female</option>
                        <option value="other">Other</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="role">Role:</label>
                    <select id="role" name="role" required>
                        <option value="">Select your role</option>
                        <option value="artist">Artist</option>
                        <option value="customer">Customer</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Password:</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Signup</button>
            </form>
            <h5><a href="http://localhost:3000/">Back to Login Page</a></h5>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
